    • checkPrefix

      public static ResourceLocation checkPrefix​(java.lang.String name, boolean warnOverrides)
      Check a name for a domain prefix, and if not present infer it from the current active mod container.
      Parameters:
      name - The name or resource location
      warnOverrides - If true, logs a warning if domain differs from that of the currently currently active mod container
      Returns:
      The ResourceLocation with given or inferred domain
